% layout 'layout', title => 'home';
<h1>Metadata validation</h1>
<p>This site has three purposes:</p>
<ol>
  <li>Provide access to the project <%= link_to 'metadata rules' => '/rule_sets' %></li>
  <li>Allow project members to <%= link_to 'check' => '/validate' %> that their metadata complies with the specification</li>
  <li><%= link_to 'Convert' => '/convert' %> spreadsheets to SampleTab or XML format for submission to BioSamples or ENA</li>
</ol>
<p>General submission support can be found in the <a href="https://www.ebi.ac.uk/seqdb/confluence/display/FAANG/FAANG+Archive+Submission+guidelines">FAANG confluence wiki.</a></p>